show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/SBk9PT
show.description: Raghav Malhotra has just months to live, but he doesn’t want pity—he wants to rewrite his legacy. Enter Kiara Singh, a headstrong woman with her own battles. What begins as a contract marriage turns into a journey of healing, unexpected love, and one final shot at happiness. Last Goodbye is a deeply emotional tale of letting go, holding on, and the kind of love that outlives time. Watch Now !
